snippet.title: NOMAD - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
NOMAD is a serene first-person 3D platformer where you use a magical rope to traverse the body of a dormant ancient colossus in order to heal its wounds and awaken it once again. Embark on a relaxing journey of melancholy to rekindle one of nature's long-lost wonders.

Trailer Music: Andrea Brun

Itch.io Page: https://david-zheng.itch.io/nomad
